'''ArgoUML'''是一个用于绘制[[UML|UML]]图的应用软件，它用Java构造，并遵守[[开源|开源]]的[[BSD許可證|BSD协议]]。因为它本身由[[Java编程语言|Java]]构建的缘故，所以ArgoUML能运行在任何支持Java的平台上。
2003年，ArgoUML获得了《软件开发杂志》的设计和分析工具类别的年度读者选择奖（annual Readers' Choice Award）。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ddj.com/architect/184414997#designtools | title = Dr. Dobb's Readers' Choice Awards, 2003 | accessdate = 2008-08-28 | archive-date = 2008-04-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080410200816/http://www.ddj.com/architect/184414997#designtools | dead-url = no }}</ref>

ArgoUML没有完全实现UML标准<ref>{{cite web| url = http://argouml.tigris.org/documentation/umlsupport/index.html| work = ArgoUML文档| title = 与UML规范不兼容的列表| access-date = 2008-08-28| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110213073541/http://argouml.tigris.org/documentation/umlsupport/index.html| archive-date = 2011-02-13| dead-url = yes}}</ref>，同时它对某些图还不能完全支持（如[[时序图|时序图]]）。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://argouml-stats.tigris.org/documentation/manual-0.24/ch19.html | title = 第19章：ArgoUML对时序图的有限涉及 | work = ArgoUML文档 | accessdate = 2008-08-28 | archive-date = 2008-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080913032953/http://argouml-stats.tigris.org/documentation/manual-0.24/ch19.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>  当前的稳定版0.24版式对0.22的一个bug修复版，它一共修正了0.22版本的172个bug。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://argouml.tigris.org/servlets/NewsItemView?newsItemID=1828| work = ArgoUML文档| title = ArgoUML文档| accessdate = 2008-08-28| archive-date = 2018-09-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180929230117/http://argouml.tigris.org/servlets/NewsItemView?newsItemID=1828| dead-url = no}}</ref>

ArgoUML的开发因为人力缺乏而受到影响。『回退（Undo）』功能早在2003年就已经提出，而迄今未实现。

